text: Johann Grégoire is a freestyle skier from France. Johann competed in the men's moguls event at the 2002 Winter Olympics. Johann was born on October 14, 1972.Johann Grégoire == References == Category:1972 births Category:Living people Category:French skiers Category:Olympians for France Category:People from Meuse Category:Sportspeople from Grand Est
